Business mogul and philanthropist, Emeka Okonkwo aka as E-Money has sponsored “Zazu” singer’s trip to London, the United Kingdom. The self-styled ‘wahala’ musician made this known on his Instagram page. He shared photos and videos with the billionaire socialite and his wife at the airport. The ‘Zazu Zeh’ crooner appreciated E-Money for his benevolence while also showering prayers on him. Hailing his benefactor, Portable said: “God dey! Thank God!! E-money don carry me trabaye. Thank God!!   Komba teams up with Broda Shaggi in ‘Sierra Leone…     Location key for hosting comedy show – Klint Da Drunk     Five Nigerian celebrities holding political offices   “One on one, life and direct. Anyone who prays for your downfall will fall for your sake.” He continued: “Zazu! I believe in God, my phone and sub. Any disappointment is a blessing. I dey with boss, E-money. E-money of life.” Captioning his post, Portable appreciated E-money with fans who have continued to shower him love. “@iam_emoney1 Na Baba God bless you more Godfather You no go fall. Thanks to those people way dey show me love from day one ZAzuu GOD Sent … On my way to Ilu Awon Osuu I believe in God my phone and Sub any disappointment is a blessing Bizza Bizza”, he wrote.